## Project Overview
GigLao is a freelance marketplace mobile app for Laos, similar to Fastwork/Fiverr.
Built with Flutter (iOS + Android + Web) and Supabase as the backend.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: Flutter 3.x (Dart)
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage + Realtime)
- **State Management**: Riverpod (flutter_riverpod)
- **Navigation**: go_router
- **HTTP/API**: Supabase Flutter SDK only (no dio/http package needed)
- **UI**: Material 3 design system

